<br>
Enchanter Epic Mob: One of the mobs grabbed by SS was the Shissar for the enchanter epic.  Should this mob be up when CoG does Fear, I will immediatly be contacting Cassia from the Silver Daggers to see if she can organize some help from the Sacred Band and we will be yielding that mob to her, and helping in any way possible.  Due to the inconsistancy of how CoG does the planes, if it becomes necessary, I will even yeild that day to SB if they can get to the mob more efficently.  Although that will remain a last resort.  This will remain in effect until such time Cassia is able to get the Shissar to complete her epic. <br>
<br>
I see no need for discussion on this point.  Cassia has helped CoG out a lot in the past and if SS is unwilling or unable to make good on what they did, then I feel its up to us as both her friends and former raiders to help her in this.<br>
<br>
All other epic mobs will remain as before.  On a case by case basis depending on where we are, and how well we're doing at the time.  And they will be rolled on at that time.<br>
<br>
If you have any questions or ideas or need clarification please feel free to post below.  I am not, however, entertaining debate on whether this is a good idea or not.  Its how it is.  Should Cassia decide she will wait and allow CoG a chance to take it that will be her decision and her's alone.  <br>
<br>
Kellory Silverstar<br>
